data.description: Spacious Lakeview property in the sought-after Riviera community in the Keys Gate area. Built in 2021, this amazing home features over 2,600 sqft of living area with four bedrooms, two of which are Masters, three bathrooms, and a 2-car garage. Upgraded flooring and window shades can also be found throughout. You’ll love this gated community with a luxury clubhouse and pool. Call today for a private showing!
